#Html("begin")
#GenHead("begin","币港湾平台活动,币港湾,币港湾官网","关注币港湾,活动不停歇!币港湾官网为您提供互联网金融服务，是优质的互联网金融服务平台。")
#Title("周周乐【币港湾官网】")
#LoadGenCSS("/resources/gen2.0/styles/index/default")
#LoadGenCSS("/resources/gen2.0/styles/activity/lucky_lenders")
#LoadGenJS("/resources/gen2.0/scripts/activity/lucky_lenders")
#GenHead("end")
<body class="body">
    #Gen2Header("home")
    <input type="hidden" value="$!countdown" id="countdown">
    <input type="hidden" value="$!participate" id="participate">
    <div class="lucky_lenders">
        <div class="lucky_lenders_banner"></div>
        <div class="lucky_lenders_container">
            <div class="lenders_bar">
                <div class="lenders_bar_left">
                    <img src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_pack.png">
                </div>
                <div class="lenders_bar_right">
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">幸运出借人，幸运奖金跟你走！</p>
                    <p>凡在本周四成功出借的用户，即有机会成为幸运出借人，获得最高150元幸运奖金！</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lenders_winnerlist">
                #if($!participate == 'end')
                    #if($!luckyList.size() == 3)
                        <img class="lenders_wrap_pic" src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_list_wrap_3.png">
                    #elseif($!luckyList.size() == 4)
                        <img class="lenders_wrap_pic" src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_list_wrap_4.png">
                    #else
                        <img class="lenders_wrap_pic" src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_list_wrap.png">
                    #end
                #else
                    <img class="lenders_wrap_pic" src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_list_wrap.png">
                #end
                <div class="lenders_list_content">
                    #if($!participate == 'end')
                        #if($!luckyList)
                            <div class="list_from">
                                <h5>本期中奖名单</h5>
                                <div class="list_title">
                                    <div class="list_title_side" style="border-left: none;border-right: none;">
                                        中奖用户
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="list_title_side" style="border-right: none;">
                                        幸运奖金
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <ul class="list_content">
                                    #set($listIndex = 1)
                                    #foreach($list in $!luckyList)
                                        #if($listIndex % 2 == 0)
                                            <li class="list_content_even">
                                                <div class="list_content_side">$list.mobile</div>
                                                <div class="list_content_side">$list.note</div>
                                            </li>
                                        #else
                                            <li class="list_content_odd">
                                                <div class="list_content_side">$list.mobile</div>
                                                <div class="list_content_side">$list.note</div>
                                            </li>
                                        #end
                                        #set($listIndex = $listIndex + 1)
                                    #end
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        #else
                            <div class="list_null">
                                <div class="list_null_img">
                                    <img src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_null.jpg">
                                </div>
                                <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">幸运出借人，即将揭晓！</p>
                                <p>出借一下，下一个幸运儿可能就是你！</p>
                            </div>
                        #end
                    #else
                        <div class="list_null">
                            <div class="list_null_img">
                                <img src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_null.jpg">
                            </div>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">幸运出借人，即将揭晓！</p>
                            <p>出借一下，下一个幸运儿可能就是你！</p>
                        </div>
                    #end
                </div>
                <div class="lenders_list_btn">
                    #if($!participate == 'notBegin')
                        <a style="cursor: default">本期尚未开始</a>
                    #elseif($!participate == 'processing')
                        <a href="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/gen2.0/regular/list">立即参与</a>
                    #else
                        <a style="cursor: default">本期已结束</a>
                    #end
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lenders_rule">
                <img class="lenders_wrap_pic" src="$!env.get('gen.server.web')/resources/gen2.0/images/activity/2018/lucky_lenders/lucky_leder_rule_wrap.png">
                <div class="lenders_rule_text">
                    <h5>活动规则：</h5>
                    <p>1、活动时间：本周四0:00:00-24:00:00；</p>
                    <p>2、活动标的：仅限港湾计划系列标的（除新手标）；</p>
                    <p>3、活动期间，成功出借活动产品的用户可参与幸运出借人的随机抽取；</p>
                    <p>4、平台将在本周五0:00:00，公布本周四的幸运出借人名单及可获得幸运奖金金额；</p>
                    <p>5、幸运奖金将以奖励金形式发放，于活动结束后的4个工作日内发放至您的账户，请在【我的资产】-【我的奖励】中查看。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- footer -->
    #Gen2Footer()
</body>
#Html("end")